{"tid":1431634,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大台可以搞,但一搞就要係臨時議會","createTime":"2019-08-08T04:48:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T06:32:31.000Z","uid":35211,"like":101,"dislike":57,"uniUserReply":53,"replies":[{"pid":"e75de734b478d18d8997f649450e3b9ccee38794","tid":1431634,"uid":35211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T04:48:27.000Z","msg":"呢場運動中,無單一人物,派別,政黨可以有足夠代表性. 任何人出黎搶大台都會畀人屌走.<br />\n咁想儲足代表性要點呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就係溝埋做瀨尿牛丸<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n為左整合各區, 各派, 各激進程度人仕, 一定要由一個<strong>完全民選制度</strong>組一個council出黎統合各方意見, 互相<strong>公開</strong>辨論,遊說. 一有行動時各方動員!各方支援!<br />\n<br />\n港共咁想我地有大台, 麻煩諗出一個真正比大眾接受既民選議會制度畀我地跟住做.<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><br />\n大台大台, 我地就用真普選組黎佢老母大台, accept nothing less<br />\n就睇下你班仆街港共/政棍夠唔夠膽同市民討論點真普選<br />\n五大訴求,缺一不可<br />\n</blockquote>"},{"pid":"67ef0628258fe402935ed7e98b89f7fec565ce8f","tid":1431634,"uid":35211,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T04:53:29.000Z","msg":"自推5次"},{"pid":"faaae070a7d06f3dcbf29078a36a8d60fd0509f6","tid":1431634,"uid":55010,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T04:53:50.000Z","msg":"冇大台"},{"pid":"2d64ed4db2e8a522cf5a99f305cdcfe7914887db","tid":1431634,"uid":92347,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T04:57:16.000Z","msg":"支持臨時議會"},{"pid":"60de98dc8c9cb5fb8c18b0420ae2e1cb80992ddd","tid":1431634,"uid":136686,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T04:57:51.000Z","msg":"臨時議會<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n臨時立法會<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca2d314e20c42bd56ebe16c06d2a53fa90e9ec1e","tid":1431634,"uid":13308,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T05:00:11.000Z","msg":"之前係支那辦果陣已經宣佈會成立臨時立法會<br />\n依嫁順勢搞lor"},{"pid":"78a0d0323ecef318df9304270dff1245fc5f4aab","tid":1431634,"uid":167042,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T05:00:40.000Z","msg":"冇大台"},{"pid":"f2aeb42e8840443cc6660e6564d3a3e93d414fa9","tid":1431634,"uid":35211,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T05:01:31.000Z","msg":"我要真普選<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dc6200e9af6402fe77b1b714de911c01d0731dd","tid":1431634,"uid":110043,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T05:01:43.000Z","msg":"好係好<br />\n但人選點搞<br />\n搞民選？"},{"pid":"521ae625f0ce0eb72667efd2e31694fc2b5141ef","tid":1431634,"uid":35211,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"7dc6200e9af6402fe77b1b714de911c01d0731dd","tid":1431634,"uid":110043,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T05:01:43.000Z","msg":"好係好<br />\n但人選點搞<br />\n搞民選？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T05:02:59.000Z","msg":"班大台撚話要組, 佢地諗. <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n行動派係佢地提出方案之前都唔駛理<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8db844fc620eb22830fc7651d32cb94ef9e71638","tid":1431634,"uid":64743,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T05:03:15.000Z","msg":"No"},{"pid":"bb021994db84cbfd3a418aada16bc7292c06b239","tid":1431634,"uid":189157,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T05:04:02.000Z","msg":"支持<br />\n一搞就要搞香港民主共和國"},{"pid":"cffdf6a2